headline: 2 Reasons to Like EXPE and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Since April 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 121%. But one standout stock has nearly doubled the market - over the past five years, Expedia has surged 231% to $161.01 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 9.6% in the last six months thanks to its solid quarterly results, beating the S&P by 12.9%.
